The reason I have my daily driver SC is because it's the only one around in my
personal travels. It's unique, it's different, and it's me. Vintage dubs
aren't run of the mill look alike that you see everyday and I for one own one
for that reason. It was the same reason I had the ramp side Corvair truck and
the front opening Isetta, or my VolksAir compressor. Except for the purest
among us, unique is unigue.

